      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the advice. the saline spray didnt really do much though and im still feeling so stuffed up i can barely breathe. my husband has some ciprofloxacin left over from his last round of antibiotics and he said it should be fine for a sinus thing. would it be okay if i just take a couple of those to clear this up? i just really need this to go away so i can rest.",
